b <- coef(final.lm)


drawit <- function(x4=0, x5=0, x6=0, x10=0, i=1){
curve(b[1] + b[2]*x2 + b[3]*x4 + b[4]*x10 + b[5]*x5 + b[6]*x2*x4 +
        b[7]*x4*I(x2^2) + b[8]*x4*I(x2^3) + b[9]*x4*x6 + b[10]*x2*x10 +
        b[11]*x4*x5

      , add=TRUE, xname="x2", col=palette()[i])
}
